    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty balanced way to put it, i guess. but when you say it \"prioritizes ideological purity over open discourse,\" are you saying that the core tenets of the movement are fundamentally at odds with free speech? like, is the movement actually capable of being inclusive if it doesn't allow for any disagreement?",
